<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>福书 · 道路真理生命</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --deep-indigo: #1a1a3d;
    --royal-purple: #4a3a7c;
    --lavender: #9d8ec9;
    --periwinkle: #b8c4e8;
    --gold: #d4af6a;
    --paper: #f6f1e6;
    --ink: #2b2620;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, #2a2a5c 0%, var(--deep-indigo) 55%, #0f0f28 100%);
    font-family: "Songti SC", "STSong", serif;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 24px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .star {
    position: absolute;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0.6;
    animation: twinkle ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes twinkle {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.15; }
    50% { opacity: 0.85; }
  }

  .scroll {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 440px;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .scroll-rod {
    height: 22px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gold) 0%, #a87d3a 50%, var(--gold) 100%);
    border-radius: 11px;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  .scroll-rod::before, .scroll-rod::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 35%, #f0d9a0, var(--gold) 60%, #8a651f);
    top: -2px;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }
  .scroll-rod::before { left: -8px; }
  .scroll-rod::after { right: -8px; }

  .scroll-body {
    background: var(--paper);
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 15% 25%, rgba(74,58,124,0.05) 0%, transparent 40%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 85% 75%, rgba(74,58,124,0.05) 0%, transparent 40%);
    padding: 40px 28px 34px;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 40px rgba(74,58,124,0.08), 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    position: relative;
  }

  .border-frame {
    border: 2px solid var(--royal-purple);
    padding: 28px 20px 30px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .border-frame::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--lavender);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .corner {
    position: absolute;
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .corner.tl { top: -2px; left: -2px; border-right: none; border-bottom: none; }
  .corner.tr { top: -2px; right: -2px; border-left: none; border-bottom: none; }
  .corner.bl { bottom: -2px; left: -2px; border-right: none; border-top: none; }
  .corner.br { bottom: -2px; right: -2px; border-left: none; border-top: none; }

  .cross {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--royal-purple);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 30px;
    color: var(--deep-indigo);
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 0 rgba(212,175,106,0.3);
  }

  .subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--lavender);
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }

  .divider-orn {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }

  .verse-block {
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }

  .verse {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 2.1;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-align: center;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .verse .hl {
    color: var(--royal-purple);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .ref {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--lavender);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .small-div {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--periwinkle);
    font-size: 12px;
    margin: 18px 0;
  }

  .seal-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-top: 22px;
  }

  .seal {
    width: 62px;
    height: 62px;
    border: 3px solid #b3374a;
    color: #b3374a;
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
    opacity: 0.85;
    transform: rotate(-4deg);
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    padding: 4px;
  }

  .date-line {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--lavender);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="scroll">
  <div class="scroll-rod"></div>

  <div class="scroll-body">
    <div class="border-frame">
      <div class="corner tl"></div>
      <div class="corner tr"></div>
      <div class="corner bl"></div>
      <div class="corner br"></div>

      <div class="cross">✝</div>
      <div class="title">福 书</div>
      <div class="subtitle">— 道 路 · 真 理 · 生 命 —</div>

      <div class="divider-orn">❈ ❈ ❈</div>

      <div class="verse-block">
        <div class="verse">
          <span class="hl">神爱世人</span>，甚至将他的独生子赐给世人，
          叫一切<span class="hl">信他的</span>不致灭亡，反得<span class="hl">永生</span>。
        </div>
        <div class="ref">— 约 翰 福 音 三 章 十 六 节 —</div>
      </div>

      <div class="small-div">❈</div>

      <div class="verse-block">
        <div class="verse">
          耶稣说：我就是<span class="hl">道路</span>、<span class="hl">真理</span>、<span class="hl">生命</span>；
          若不藉着我，没有人能到父那里去。
        </div>
        <div class="ref">— 约 翰 福 音 十 四 章 六 节 —</div>
      </div>

      <div class="seal-row">
        <div class="seal">信心盼望</div>
        <div class="seal">恩典同在</div>
      </div>

      <div class="date-line">谨 此 为 记</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="scroll-rod" style="margin-top: -4px;"></div>
</div>

<script>
  const container = document.body;
  for (let i = 0; i < 60; i++) {
    const s = document.createElement('div');
    s.className = 'star';
    const size = Math.random() * 2 + 1;
    s.style.width = size + 'px';
    s.style.height = size + 'px';
    s.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
    s.style.top = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
    s.style.animationDuration = (2 + Math.random() * 3) + 's';
    s.style.animationDelay = Math.random() * 3 + 's';
    container.appendChild(s);
  }
</script>

</body>
</html>
